Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.74,0:00:22.68,Shiver,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,1000)\blur0.6\pos(200,20)}Everything that was right
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.80,0:00:25.50,Shiver,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,1000)\blur0.6\pos(630,20)}We both enjoyed a good fight
