Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.63,0:00:30.44,Shiver,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,1000)\blur0.6\pos(280,20)}All the holes we had to breathe
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.56,0:00:33.46,Shiver,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,1000)\blur0.6\pos(805,20)}To make the other one leave
